{"id":1490,"date":"2023-11-02T16:07:01","date_gmt":"2023-11-02T20:07:01","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/manninglaw.com\/?page_id=1490"},"modified":"2023-11-02T16:15:50","modified_gmt":"2023-11-02T20:15:50","slug":"manning-law-firm-associate-attorney-clarke-martin-recently-attended-the-north-carolina-state-bars-legal-deserts-summit","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/manninglaw.com\/in-the-news\/manning-law-firm-associate-attorney-clarke-martin-recently-attended-the-north-carolina-state-bars-legal-deserts-summit\/","title":{"rendered":"Manning Law Firm Associate Attorney Clarke Martin recently attended the North Carolina State Bar\u2019s Legal Deserts Summit"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><strong>MANNING LAW FIRM ASSOCIATE ATTORNEY CLARKE MARTIN RECENTLY ATTENDED THE NORTH CAROLINA STATE BAR\u2019S LEGAL DESERTS SUMMIT<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Manning Law Firm Associate Attorney Clarke Martin recently attended the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=pBNTuHwi27E\">North Carolina State <br>Bar\u2019s Legal Deserts Summit<\/a>. There, some of our State\u2019s brightest and most passionate public<br>interest lawyers brainstormed ways to reduce the number of people in North Carolina whose<br>legal needs go unmet due to a lack of lawyers in their geographic area or practice area. A &#8220;legal<br>desert&#8221; is defined as a county which has fewer than one attorney for every 1,000 residents. In<br>North Carolina, 48 counties fit this definition despite having experienced a population growth of<br>almost one million residents over the last decade (2010-2020). Another type of legal desert is a<br>practice area: if most of the attorneys in a given area practice X type of law but a client has a<br>legal issue which falls into Y practice area, that client may be experiencing a legal desert even<br>in a major metropolitan area.<br><br>Martin said: \u201cIf you look statewide in the state of North Carolina we are in a crisis in that there<br>are not enough people practicing criminal law anywhere.\u201d Martin noted the fulfilling nature of<br>her work, calling it \u201cconstitutionally mandated\u201d and \u201cimportant\u201d. She values working with and<br>helping people one-on-one and \u201cachiev[ing] something for someone every day[.]\u201d<br><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Attorney Clarke Martin\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" src=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/2rCLLY4ACFs?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen><\/iframe>\n<\/div><\/figure>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>MANNING LAW FIRM ASSOCIATE ATTORNEY CLARKE MARTIN RECENTLY ATTENDED THE NORTH CAROLINA STATE BAR\u2019S LEGAL DESERTS SUMMIT Manning Law Firm Associate Attorney Clarke Martin recently attended the North Carolina State Bar\u2019s Legal Deserts Summit. There, some of our State\u2019s brightest and most passionate publicinterest lawyers brainstormed ways to reduce the number of people in North&#8230; <a class=\"excerpt-read-more\" href=\"https:\/\/manninglaw.com\/in-the-news\/manning-law-firm-associate-attorney-clarke-martin-recently-attended-the-north-carolina-state-bars-legal-deserts-summit\/\" title=\"ReadManning Law Firm Associate Attorney Clarke Martin recently attended the North Carolina State Bar\u2019s Legal Deserts Summit\">Read more &raquo;<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":4,"featured_media":0,"parent":1375,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-1490","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"acf":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with th